{"tid":1676860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抗暴之戰】警方新規定！跑步要申請不反對通知書 議員震驚：衰過大陸","createTime":"2019-10-26T17:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T17:39:45.000Z","uid":38954,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f8df98e9263b09570a99503c9ec6449a15678423","tid":1676860,"uid":38954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T17:04:19.000Z","msg":"監控之爪，由遊行集會，伸延至民間康體活動。有跑會負責人向《蘋果》表示，上周二（22日）收到警方口頭和電郵通知，日後所有在公眾地方進行的跑步訓練，均需在活動舉行前7天申請「不反對通知書」，並要清楚交代活動時間、地點、路線，以及活動後聚餐的地點。該跑會一度把恒常練跑活動改稱「祈禱會」，但不少參加者仍被嚇怕，紛紛退出訓練。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本地跑會「香港長跑網」逢周四在馬鞍山運動場進行跑步訓練，參加者於活動後再到區內餐廳用膳。負責人Alan指，由於活動費用全免，參加者可即場報名且名額不限，參加人數最高峯時多達60多人，每周活動照片會上載至網站和facebook專頁。<br />\n<br />\n不過，Alan稱上周一（21日）突然收到警察交通總部聯絡，稱欲了解跑步活動內容；周二再收到警察牌照課來電和發出的電郵，聲稱收到交通總部轉介，提醒該會根據《公安條例》，任何在公路、大道或公園舉行，而出席人數超過30人的公眾遊行，主辦團體須最少要7天前以書面方式，由組織人或其代表親自交予警署，知會警務處處長有關活動。<br />\n<br />\nAlan指，警方聲稱即使在運動場練跑，也要向警方提供時間、路線和活動後聚餐的地點。他即日向警方申報周四晚、預計約50人參與的恒常跑步活動，並提供活動後用膳的地點，惟至活動當日仍未獲警方發出「不反對通知書」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191027/60195604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191027%2F60195604&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=16d9becc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191027%2F60195604&h=eff7e02c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191027/60195604</a>"},{"pid":"0ec9dc94de6a2e9e234812829f405fe49f5636ee","tid":1676860,"uid":305579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T17:05:04.000Z","msg":"［極重要］咪撚推哩個po！！害死手足！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1676826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1676826</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2f865e95a4f391d28dd97802b3dfcf69b4465d7e","tid":1676860,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T17:05:07.000Z","msg":"互相尊重。和諧共存<br />\n10/27 九龍宗教集會<br />\n下午三點 梳士巴利花園 保護宗教自由<br />\n#Weconnect #FreeHK #StandWithHK<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ry26uKc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fry26uKc.png&h=344de0d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59c9b31cf13bb0a992d5488dc0daaa14585fc633","tid":1676860,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T17:05:14.000Z","msg":"以我所知，有唔少有錢佬都有跑開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好多都係離地撚"},{"pid":"a4b4a7b16c4b007695038740a5ce1e8ce6c33b51","tid":1676860,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T17:05:26.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"6cbe4f73f9194688bcebb6396e0a93ad627f3e5a","tid":1676860,"uid":256620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T17:06:08.000Z","msg":"ONL99<br />\n721.831"},{"pid":"ebecbf30235716e0bd26f6b01a7bb3af3852d643","tid":1676860,"uid":315584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T17:06:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/P4xKe00.gif\" />"},{"pid":"d03786cb0a72014e7c4b5c03ff68e07facbb00bd","tid":1676860,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T17:06:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1540defdd22bc5a69628a2383ac1df5c84b6dbf5","tid":1676860,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T17:07:39.000Z","msg":"Police state<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1ef7f14a90139e8bd4a8d074353592c641bf96","tid":1676860,"uid":274538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T17:07:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aJ4D5iQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaJ4D5iQ.jpg&h=5596c7c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fua7YD